<section class="cta-section" id="cta">
  <div class="inner">
    <p class="eyebrow">Kostenlos &amp; unverbindlich</p>
    <h2>Zeig uns deinen Betrieb. Wir machen dich schlagkräftiger als jedes Team ohne KI.</h2>
    <p class="subtext">
      Standardlösung oder individuell gebaut — wir finden was für deinen Betrieb passt. 30 Minuten. Kostenlos. Ohne Versprechen die wir nicht halten.
    </p>
    <a href="https://calendly.com/onlinemaster711/new-meeting" class="btn-cta" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Jetzt kostenloses Gespräch buchen</a>
    <p class="cta-hint">📅 Direkt in den Kalender – kein Telefonat nötig</p>
  </div>

  <div class="cta-deco" aria-hidden="true"></div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--primary-container));
    padding: 6rem 0;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .inner {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--primary-fixed);
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3.5vw, 2.5rem);
    line-height: 1.25;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .subtext {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    max-width: 54ch;
  }

  .btn-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--secondary), var(--secondary-container));
    color: var(--on-secondary);
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(184, 0, 73, 0.35);
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .btn-cta:hover {
    opacity: 0.9;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .cta-hint {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
  }

  /* Decorative blurred circle */
  .cta-deco {
    position: absolute;
    width: 500px;
    height: 500px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(223, 230, 200, 0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
    border-radius: 50%;
    top: -100px;
    right: -100px;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
</style>
